  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个广播任务的状态流转图。管理员创建广播有两种场景：一种是创建远期广播，另一种是立即广播。远期广播应该先从WorkerNode进入SCHEDULED状态，而立即广播直接从IngressController进入PREPARING状态。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Infra_WorkerNode",
        "SCHEDULED",
        "Infra_IngressController",
        "PREPARING",
        "Admin"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了。那SCHEDULED到PREPARING的流转是由预计算调度器触发的对吗？另外，管理员在SCHEDULED和PREPARING阶段都能取消任务？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "SCHEDULED",
        "PREPARING",
        "CANCELLED",
        "Pre-computation scheduler"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对的。PREPARING阶段会异步拉取用户数据，成功就进入READY，失败则进入FAILED。READY之后由激活调度器推进到ACTIVE，这里也要经过IngressController。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "PREPARING",
        "READY",
        "FAILED",
        "ACTIVE",
        "Infra_IngressController",
        "Async user fetch",
        "Activation scheduler"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我把PREPARING到READY、FAILED的流转加上，还有READY到ACTIVE的路径。ACTIVE之后呢？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "PREPARING",
        "READY",
        "FAILED",
        "ACTIVE"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "ACTIVE状态有三种出口：正常过期走EXPIRED，管理员通过API取消走CANCELLED，还有一种特殊情况——如果是群组广播，消费DLT事件会进入FAILED。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "ACTIVE",
        "EXPIRED",
        "CANCELLED",
        "FAILED",
        "Expiration scheduler",
        "DLT event",
        "group broadcast"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "确认一下，EXPIRED、CANCELLED、FAILED都是终态吗？它们需要落到具体的 infra 组件上吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "EXPIRED",
        "CANCELLED",
        "FAILED",
        "Infra_RedisCache",
        "Infra_EtcdCluster"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "是的。EXPIRED和FAILED都落到RedisCache做缓存清理，CANCELLED落到EtcdCluster做状态持久化。另外READY阶段管理员也能取消。",
